OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775045470
OL,3,CBBC apologises over separate
OL,4,Callegations about Scott Mills made
OL,5,Clast year
OL,7,FThe BBC received unspecified
OL,8,Fallegations about Radio DJ Scott Mills
OL,9,F"messaging someone inappropriately"
OL,10,Flast year, but did not ask further
OL,11,Fquestions, a journalist has said.
OL,13,FFormer presenter Anna Brees told The
OL,14,FTelegraph she got in touch with the
OL,15,FBBC in May 2025 to say she had
OL,16,Freceived information about alleged
OL,17,F"inappropriate communications"
OL,18,Finvolving Mills.
OL,26,@yD@AOUyD@^O]
