OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775045470
OL,3,CBBC apologises over separate
OL,4,Callegations about Scott Mills made
OL,5,Clast year
OL,7,FThe incident is not related to
OL,8,Fallegations of "serious sexual
OL,9,Foffences" against a teenage boy that
OL,10,FMills, 53, was investigated for in
OL,11,F2016.
OL,13,FBrees said: "Someone who knew I used
OL,14,Fto work for the BBC volunteered some
OL,15,Finformation about Scott Mills
OL,16,Fmessaging someone inappropriately.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
