CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775045470
OL,3,CBBC apologises over separate
OL,4,Callegations about Scott Mills made
OL,5,Clast year
OL,7,F"It was a credible source and I was
OL,8,Fconcerned so I decided to contact the
OL,9,FBBC to make them aware of it and see
OL,10,Fif they came back with anything. I
OL,11,Fdidn't get a response."
OL,13,FThe BBC apologised on Tuesday for its
OL,14,Flack of action, confirming that it
OL,15,Freceived a press enquiry in 2025 that
OL,16,F"included limited information".
OL,18,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
