OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775045470
OL,3,CBBC apologises over separate
OL,4,Callegations about Scott Mills made
OL,5,Clast year
OL,7,F"This should have been followed up and
OL,8,Fwe should have asked further
OL,9,Fquestions," a spokesperson for the BBC
OL,10,Fsaid in a statement shared with ITV
OL,11,FNews.
OL,13,F"We apologise for this and will look
OL,14,Finto why this did not happen."
OL,16,FMills was reportedly sacked from his
OL,17,FBBC Radio 2 job on Monday over
OL,18,Fallegations relating to "personal
OL,19,Fconduct".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
