OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775045470
OL,3,CBBC apologises over separate
OL,4,Callegations about Scott Mills made
OL,5,Clast year
OL,7,FThe Metropolitan Police said on
OL,8,FTuesday that Mills was investigated in
OL,9,F2016 in relation to alleged "serious
OL,10,Fsexual offences against a teenage
OL,11,Fboy", telling ITV News the victim was
OL,12,Funder 16.
OL,14,FThe specific age of the victim cannot
OL,15,Fbe given due to the risk of jigsaw
OL,16,Fidentification, the police said.
OL,18,FMills has not publicly commented on
OL,19,Fthe allegations and was last on air on
OL,20,FTuesday last week.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
