PN,30606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775045470
OL,3,CBBC apologises over separate
OL,4,Callegations about Scott Mills made
OL,5,Clast year
OL,7,F"In December 2016, the Met began an
OL,8,Finvestigation following a referral
OL,9,Ffrom another police force," the police
OL,10,Fsaid in a statement.
OL,12,F"The investigation related to
OL,13,Fallegations of serious sexual offences
OL,14,Fagainst a teenage boy. These were
OL,15,Freported to taken place between 1997
OL,16,Fand 2000.
OL,18,F"As part of these enquiries, a man who
OL,19,Fwas in his 40s at the time of the
OL,20,Finterview, was questioned by police
OL,21,Funder caution in July 2018.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775045470
OL,3,CBBC apologises over separate
OL,4,Callegations about Scott Mills made
OL,5,Clast year
OL,7,F"A full file of evidence was submitted
OL,8,Fto the Crown Prosecution Service, who
OL,9,Fdetermined the evidential threshold
OL,10,Fhad not been met to bring charges.
OL,11,FFollowing this advice, the
OL,12,Finvestigation was closed in May 2019."
OL,14,FIn an internal note on Monday morning,
OL,15,FLorna Clarke, director of music at the
OL,16,FBBC informed staff that Mills had left
OL,17,Fthe broadcaster.
OL,19,F"I know that this news will be sudden
OL,20,Fand unexpected and therefore must come
OL,21,Fas a shock," Clarke said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
