OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775045470
OL,3,CBBC apologises over separate
OL,4,Callegations about Scott Mills made
OL,5,Clast year
OL,7,F"Not least as so many of us have
OL,8,Fworked with Scott over a great many
OL,9,Fyears, across a broad range of our
OL,10,Fprogrammes on R1, 5Live, R2 and TV. I
OL,11,Ffelt it was important to share this
OL,12,Fnews with you at the earliest
OL,13,Fopportunity.
OL,15,F"Of course, it will also come as a
OL,16,Fshock to our audience and loyal
OL,17,Fbreakfast show listeners too. I will
OL,18,Fupdate everyone with more information
OL,19,Fon plans for the show when I'm able to.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775045470
OL,3,CBBC apologises over separate
OL,4,Callegations about Scott Mills made
OL,5,Clast year
OL,7,F"While I appreciate many of you will
OL,8,Fhave questions, I hope you can
OL,9,Funderstand that I am not going to be
OL,10,Fsaying anything further now."
OL,12,FMills had been working on the BBC
OL,13,FRadio 2 breakfast show since taking
OL,14,Fover from Zoe Ball in January 2025.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
