OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775045470
OL,3,CBBC apologises over separate
OL,4,Callegations about Scott Mills made
OL,5,Clast year
OL,7,FHe began his BBC career on Radio 1 in
OL,8,Fthe late 1990s as the early breakfast
OL,9,Fhost, before going on to present
OL,10,Fweekend slots and then an early
OL,11,Fevening show while providing maternity
OL,12,Fcover for Sara Cox. When Cox did not
OL,13,Freturn, the programme was renamed The
OL,14,FScott Mills Show.
OL,16,FIn 2022, Mills joined Radio 2,
OL,17,Freplacing Steve Wright in his weekday
OL,18,Fafternoon slot.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
