OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775045470
OL,3,CBBC apologises over separate
OL,4,Callegations about Scott Mills made
OL,5,Clast year
OL,7,FMills was dropped by child cancer
OL,8,Fcharity Neuroblastoma UK, where he was
OL,9,Fa patron, after news of his dismissal
OL,10,Fbroke.
OL,12,F"Neuroblastoma UK have taken the
OL,13,Fdecision to part ways with Scott
OL,14,FMills, and he is no longer a patron of
OL,15,Four charity," the organisation said in
OL,16,Fa statement.
OL,18,F"We have communicated this decision to
OL,19,FScott and his team, and would like to
OL,20,Fthank him for his support to date."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
